{"tid":1559054,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全民運動年，做運動啦香港人","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:08:19.000Z","uid":259033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b524fb04d13ac7e10dfb2c9089a684c9226862d","tid":1559054,"uid":259033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:08:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558369\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558369</a><br />\n小弟十分認同上面既意見，但要保護人，前提係要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有能力，有體力</span></span></span>提議大家以後保持健康生活，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">早睡早起</span></span>，提早起身跑步，如果要為生活番工，就早啲起身，罷搭港鐵，搭巴士，行多啲，打吾贏都要走得快，吾好成為前線既負擔。可以既就去做下gym，打下拳，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">吾好講咩無時間</span></strong></span>，時間係擠出黎，吾好打機，吾好宅係屋企，宅係張床做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">廢青</span></span>，而家打仗呀，你當去shopping 呀?X你! 無錯啲黑警係有專業訓練，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個吾係我地弱既藉口</span></span>，起碼要將<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">差距縮少</span></span>。絲打亦一樣，點解黑警專捉你地?因為女仔天生體力較弱（非歧視），以弱入手係必然，所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">女仔更應練跑</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跑得快先吾會比人針對，吾洗怕會腳粗，女仔天生就比較少肌肉，亦難以操大啲肌肉。</span></span>，而且腳型都會靚啲（本人非變態）。總之，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做運動一定無死，呢個係持久戰，無體力無體能又點同正苦，同淋病鬥?</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 9人喪生<br />\n2. 3人眼睛受傷<br />\n3. 2次地鐵站恐怖攻擊<br />\n4. 2人被黑道份子砍成重傷<br />\n5. 1183人被捕<br />\n6. 超過100人被控罪</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JvvEBYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJvvEBYN.jpg&h=c8e05b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地吾可以收貨，犧牲者們吾會原諒我地<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人加油！！！！<br />\n願榮光歸香港！！！</strong></span></span>"}]}